T02TD2641E:245b-1: pradzny'a p'a ra mi ta hri da ya s'a dha nam n'a ma /
T02TD2641E:245b-3: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i snying po'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba /
T02TD2641E:245b-4: bcom ldan 'das ma shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2641E:245b-5: gang zhig sngon du byas gyur pas //
T02TD2641E:245b-6: rab zhi thams cad mkhyen mdzad pa'i //
T02TD2641E:245b-7: rgyal ba de la rab btud de //
T02TD2641E:245b-8: sgrub thabs cho ga dran par bya //
T02TD2641E:245b-9: dben zhing nyams dga'i sa phyogs su //
T02TD2641E:245b-10: bde ba'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
T02TD2641E:245b-11: snying gar pad zla'i nyi steng du //
T02TD2641E:245b-13: rgyal ba sras bcas spyan drangs te //
T02TD2641E:245b-14: nam mkha'i phyogs su gnas par bsam //
T02TD2641E:245b-15: mchod dang nyes pa bshags par bya //
T02TD2641E:245b-16: rjes su yi rang gsol ba gdab //
T02TD2641E:245b-17: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed blang bya zhing //
T02TD2641E:245b-18: byang chub chen por bsngo bar bya //
T02TD2641E:245b-19: byams dang snying rje dga' ba dang //
T02TD2641E:245b-20: btang snyoms tshangs pa'i gnas pa bsgom//
T02TD2641E:245b-21: gsang sngags 'di ni rab tu bzlas //
T02TD2641E:245b-22: aom sva bh'a wa shuddha:sarba dharmm'a:sva bh'a wa shuddho& ham /
T02TD2641E:245b-23: rgyu dang mi rgyu 'di dag kun //
T02TD2641E:245b-24: gzod nas rang bzhin stong par dran //
T02TD2641E:245b-25: de rjes stong pa'i rang bzhin las //
T02TD2641E:245b-26: yam ram bam lam 'byung ba bzhi //
T02TD2641E:245b-27: sum las ri rab de steng du //
T02TD2641E:245b-28: bhr'um las mdzes pa'i gzhal yas khang ;
T02TD2641E:245b-29: / yangs shing rgyan ldan bsam par bya //
T02TD2641E:245b-30: dbus su seng ge'i khri steng du //
T02TD2641E:245b-31: padma nyi ma la gnas pa'i //
T02TD2641E:245b-32: dmar ser rgyal yum sku mdog ser //
T02TD2641E:245b-33: zhal gcig phyag bzhi sku ni rgyas //
T02TD2641E:245b-34: g-yas gnyis rdo rje skyabs sbyin can //
T02TD2641E:245b-35: g-yon gnyis rdo rje chos 'chad mdzad //
T02TD2641E:246a-2: shar du seng ge zla steng du //
T02TD2641E:246a-3: sam las rgyal ba sh'akya thub //
T02TD2641E:246a-4: btso ma'i mdog can sprul pa'i sku //
T02TD2641E:246a-5: gtsug tor ldan pa bskyed par bya //
T02TD2641E:246a-6: nub tu padma zla ba la //
T02TD2641E:246a-7: hr'i: las 'jig rten dbang phyug ni //
T02TD2641E:246a-8: shin tu dkar zhing rgyan mdzes pa //
T02TD2641E:246a-9: sems dpa'i skyil krung bzhugs par bsam //
T02TD2641E:246a-10: lho ru mam las sh'a ri'i bu //
T02TD2641E:246a-11: dka' thub cha byad sku mdog ni //
T02TD2641E:246a-12: dmar skya pus btsugs thal mo sbyar //
T02TD2641E:246a-13: shin tu mdzes pa'i sku nyid bsam //
T02TD2641E:246a-14: byang du kunda las bskyed pa //
T02TD2641E:246a-15: dmar po rgyal la gus pa'i tshul //
T02TD2641E:246a-16: padma'i steng du bskyed byas nas //
T02TD2641E:246a-17: de ltar bskyed pa rdzogs pa dang //
T02TD2641E:246a-18: bdag nyid thugs ka'i mam las ni //
T02TD2641E:246a-20: mchod dang dza: h'um bam ho: yis //
T02TD2641E:246a-21: so sor dgug gzhug byas nas ni //
T02TD2641E:246a-22: rgyal bas dbang bskur so so la //
T02TD2641E:246a-23: rnam snang mi bskyod rin 'byung dang //
T02TD2641E:246a-24: mtha' yas rgyal ba nyid kyis mtshan //
T02TD2641E:246a-25: yi ge gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs //
T02TD2641E:246a-26: yum gyi thugs kar rgyal ba nyid //
T02TD2641E:246a-27: bsdus te ting 'dzin snyoms zhugs nas //
T02TD2641E:246a-28: dris dang lan gdab stong pa'i don //
T02TD2641E:246a-29: 'khor rnams kun la sbyin par bsam //
T02TD2641E:246a-30: 'di ltar chos kun rab zhi las //
T02TD2641E:246a-31: spros pa'i 'khor kun yum la bsdu //
T02TD2641E:246a-32: mtshan bcas ting 'dzin yi ge la //
T02TD2641E:246a-33: dmigs te gsal la mi rtog bya //
T02TD2641E:246a-34: gzod nas zhi ba'i chos kun ni //
T02TD2641E:246a-35: rkyen dbang 'khrul bar rab snad la //
T02TD2641E:246a-36: de nyid tshe na zhi ba nyid //
T02TD2641E:246a-37: zhi tshe sgyu ma lta bur snang //
T02TD2641E:246a-38: mtha' bzhir mi rtog bral bar min //
T02TD2641E:246a-39: bying rgod mi gnas sems nyid ni //
T02TD2641E:246a-40: 'od gsal cir yang mi sgom pa //
T02TD2641E:246a-41: mtshams med rnal 'byor pha rol phyin //
T02TD2641E:246a-42: rgyal bas zhi bar rab gsungs dang //
T02TD2641E:246a-43: gcig dang du ma bral sogs pas //
T02TD2641E:246a-44: spros pa bkag pas mi rtog shes //
T02TD2641E:246a-45: rnam par rtog dang yang dag rtog / gal te skyo na bzlas bya ste //
T02TD2641E:246a-47: aom ga te ga te p'a ra ga te p'a ra sam ga te bo dhi sv'a h'a /
T02TD2641E:246a-48: mam la rab bskor 'od zer ni //
T02TD2641E:246a-49: spro bsdus don byas sngags kyi 'od //
T02TD2641E:246a-50: lte ba'i kha yi bar du bskor //
T02TD2641E:246a-51: ye shes sems dpa' mchod la gshegs //
T02TD2641E:246a-52: stong pa bco brgyad brjod bya ste //
T02TD2641E:246a-53: dam tshig sems dpa' thams cad dang //
T02TD2641E:246b-0: gzhal yas khang ni mi @246b dmigs bya //
T02TD2641E:246b-1: rgyal ba'i bka' dang n'a g'a rdzu na yi //
T02TD2641E:246b-2: gsungs pa la brten mos rnams don dang ni //
T02TD2641E:246b-3: bdag nyid sbyang phyir cho ga thabs mchog byas //
T02TD2641E:246b-4: mkhas rnams blo yi dri ma bzod par mdzod //
T02TD2641E:246b-5: 'di la ngal ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba des //
T02TD2641E:246b-6: 'gro rnams rab sbyangs snying po'i don shes nas //
T02TD2641E:246b-7: rgyal ba'i go 'phang rab tu thob 'gyur te //
T02TD2641E:246b-8: 'gro rnams zhi ba'i lam la 'god par shog / shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i sgrub thabs slob dpon chen po d'a ri ka pas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
